E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~A motherfucking subway train! Oh yeah, baby.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~一辆牛逼哄哄的列车！哦耶，宝贝。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Okay. You just need to jump on the train. Climb to the front and unhook the lead car. I'll take it from there.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~好了。你只要跳上列车，爬到前面解挂车头。剩下的我来。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~I got you that tank thing and the chopper - what now, you want the Statue of Happiness for your back yard?
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~我给你弄来了坦克和直升机，然后呢？是不是要把幸福女神像放进后院？

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~I see myself getting cut in half or locked up, bro - that's what I see.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~眼前只有身首异处的尸体和监狱，兄弟。我看到了这些。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~I thought the world liked us now!
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~我以为现在全世界都喜欢我们了！

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Okay, we just need the front car of the train.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~好的，我们只需要列车的车头。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Yusuf. Where are you, man? They think I'm a fucking terrorist.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~Yusuf，你在哪？他们当我是恐怖分子了。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Chill out, homie. Yusuf's on his way.
~z~You, Tony Gayer and a camel getting all velvet rope on some Arabic shit.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~你、基佬Tony和一个阿拉伯人，在阿拉伯盛大开业。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~We haven't got all day. Unhook the front car.
~z~I have to go now, man. Wait here above the tracks.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~我得走了，兄弟。在轨道上等着吧。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~I hope you got your work shoes on.
~z~Be my guest, bro. You jump on the train and I'll put my feet up.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~请便吧，兄弟。你跳上车顶我就能休息了。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~made of models on a track made of gold.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~穿过黄金轨道上的模型隧道。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~You got choppers on my ass too?
~z~The prize of the fleet. The assfucking flagship of the LTA. Give it up!
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~他们的宝贝。LTA的宝贝列车。归我了！

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~I guess I better wait for that motherfucker.
~z~Aside from how fucking dumb that sounds, how am I supposed to take that thing?
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~先不说这想法有多蠢，你告诉我怎么抢地铁？

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~I fucking love you, man. I love you. See you later.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~我他妈爱死你了，兄弟，我爱你。一会儿见。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~What you need a chopper for, cop?
~z~Yo. How am I supposed to pull this off?
~z~You jump on board, you climb to the front and you unhook the car.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~你跳上车顶，爬到车头，解开车钩。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Can't you just buy yourself a subway car, bro?
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~你就不能自己买一辆吗，老兄？

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Would you shut the fuck up, man? What's wrong with you?
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~你能不能闭嘴啊，伙计？你到底啥毛病？

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Here I come, baby. You better be gripping tight.
~z~Get in position to jump, my friend. I will meet you later.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~准备好跳下去吧，我的朋友。一会儿再见了。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~No, man, shit. We need the genuine article. The real deal.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~不行。妈的，我们要的是原汁原味。是真品。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Hey man, I missed the train, bro. You're gonna have to rethink things.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，我错过列车了，兄弟。你可能得重新规划了。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~I'm here, Yusuf. Where the fuck are you?
~z~Don't joke around with that weapon, dog.
~z~I wish I was coming with you, man. I'd be one crazy motherfucker on that train.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~我真的想和你一起去，伙计。我也想当车顶上的那个疯子。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~You doing worse to this train than I am.
~z~But he's obsessed with what they won't sell him.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~但他更中意自己买不到的东西。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Okay, man, okay. Back to the drawing board. Call me.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，兄弟，好吧。我再研究研究。有事打电话。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Yo, I'm Dominican. We ain't terrorists, you dumb fucks.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~哟，我是多米尼加良民。不是恐怖分子，你们这些蠢货。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~I don't think I'm going to get this bitch.
~z~Before I forget, you mind handing over some more of those explosive shells? Those things are tight, man.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~差点忘了，你能再给我些爆炸子弹吗？那玩意太猛了，兄弟。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~You think we could put the Amir name to anything but authentic shit?
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~你觉得能把我Amir的名字写在水货上吗？

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~No one likes people fucking with their public transport in this paranoid age.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~在这个多疑的时代，大家都讨厌打公共交通主意的人。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~You kidding me? Where were they hiding?
~z~You know what, I can drive to the chopper later. Take us to the Broker side of the Algonquin bridge now.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~听着，待会儿我自己去拿直升机。现在先去Algonquin大桥的Broker段。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Yusuf, bro. Hand over some more exploding shotgun shells. I love those things.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~Yusuf兄弟，再给我点爆炸子弹吧。我爱死它了。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Shit, man, I was already playing subway conductor in my head. Too fucking lame. Call me soon.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，伙计，我都在脑补自己当列车长了。太糟了。有空联系。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~I don't know why I hang out with you, bro.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~都不知道我为什么要跟你混在一起，兄弟。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~They invented math and shit. I'm here I'm not afraid. I can get my hands dirty. I can work.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~他们还创造了数学。我不怕下工地。我能干这活。我可以的。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~We can always get a new car.
~z~We rolling out to the Broker side of the Algonquin bridge, homeboy.
~z~What the fuck am I getting into, man? Shit.
~z~Okay, cool man, listen, it was good catching up with you, okay? I'll see you soon.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~好，那挺好。听着，很高兴又碰到你，好吗？我先告辞了。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~The plan doesn't allow for that, homie. Disappoints me as much as you. Probably more. Inside, I am crying.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~可惜计划不允许啊，哥们儿。我可能比你更失望。在我心里，我已经哭了。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~There might even be room for a Maisonette 9 franchise there. How about it?
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~说不定还能在那儿开一家9号豪宅的分店。你说怎么样？

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Well you know it's my father...uh...hey, you know my ancestors, we built the pyramids baby! We built the ziggurats.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，其实是我爸他...嘿，说说我祖先吧。我们建造了金字塔！我们创造了神迹。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Have fun with it, you crazy fool.
~z~Cynics don't build pyramids, man. You got to believe. Tell me you believe, Luis.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~悲观的人造不出金字塔。你得相信它。告诉我你信了，Luis。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~That and I'm going to put your clubs on the world stage.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~而且我还要让你们的夜店走向世界。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~I'm going in for the kill. Hold on!
~z~Yusuf, bro, we got problems, man. I couldn't handle that thing for you.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~Yusuf，兄弟。出了一点岔子，兄弟。我不能帮你了。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Head out to the east side of the Algonquin Bridge, my dude.
~z~Where the fuck did they come from?
~z~The train is not just for me. It will be the centerpiece of a new Liberty themed development in the Gulf.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~这车不是我弄来玩的。它会成为海湾地区新开发项目的核心，以自由城为主题。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~They called Michelangelo crazy, but he invented the wheel and who's laughing now?
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~他们说米开朗基罗是疯子，但他发明了车轮。是谁笑到了最后啊？

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~I'm gonna look after you. You and Tony. Your problems, man, Yusuf can make them go away.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~我会照顾好你们的。你和Tony。你们的问题，兄弟，Yusuf能解决掉的。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~You better be able to, bro. 'Cause you about to owe me big time.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~你最好能办到，兄弟。因为你欠我太多了。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Ever since I played with my golden train set as a child, I have always wanted one and now we're gonna get it.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~小时候玩过我的黄金小火车以后，我就一直想要一台。现在就要弄到手了。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~I told you I was getting one of these.
~z~Check this out, a genuine LTA submarine train!
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~看看这个，原汁原味的LTA海底列车！

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~I'm crafting this whole thing with my bare hands.
~z~This is where you going to jump.
~z~Believe it, baby. Pinch yourself. You ain't dreaming. This is no film. The city is our playground, homie.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~快醒醒，掐掐你自己。你没有做梦。这不是拍电影。自由城就是我们的游乐场，哥们儿。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~I'll handle all the rest. Real simple, man.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~剩下的交给我。很简单的，兄弟。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~But I thought you was busy building the pyramids?
~z~Greatest heist in Liberty City history. Look at us, man! We're the biggest pimps in the city.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~自由城史上最大的劫案。看看我们，兄弟！我们是自由城最大的坏蛋。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~This is where the city's budget goes?
~z~Just get me on the fucking ground!
~z~"The impossible dream. Priceless indulgence. Style by Yusuf Amir. A timeless classic. Timeless classic!"
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~「无尽的奢华，不可能之梦。Yusuf Amir风格。万古千秋的经典。永恒的经典！」

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~'Cause you fucking love this shit, homie. Ain't nothing like rolling with this Arabic bad boy.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~因为你喜欢这种活，哥们儿。跟着阿拉伯坏小子混可是独一份的。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Okay, shit, if I do help you, what's the plan?
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，操。如果我要帮你，计划是什么？

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Excellent idea, my friend, but that will have to wait.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~很好的主意，我的朋友，但那得往后稍稍。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~People will write a bible about this shit in the future, baby.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~以后会有人据此写本圣经的，宝贝。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, sounds perfect, man. Just what the people want right now. But...
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~听起来真不错，兄弟。很符合当代人的需求。但是...

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Shit, dude, you got attitude. Ease off with that thing.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~操了，兄弟，给点面子。别乱打了。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~You heard me. A genuine Liberty City subway car.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~你没听错。货真价实的自由城地铁。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Tell me you fucking see it - me and you riding in our very own subway train through a tunnel
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~告诉我你看到了——我和你坐在我们自己的列车上，

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Why do I struggle to believe that?
~z~Come on, man. Uncouple the front car.
~z~Yo, could you give me a ride to my helicopter? I could tell you something on the way.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~哟，你可以送我去我家停机坪吗？我在路上和你详细说明。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~It's going to be drowned in gold, y'know it's like, 'yo, yo, is that a diamond in your pocket or are you just pleased to see me', and shit.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~这里会变成金山。怎么说来着，「哟哟哟，你是突发横财了，还是见到我太高兴了。」

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~That's my boy! There's the reason you're my main hombre.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~这才对嘛！这才是我的好哥们儿。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~You got some exercise plans for me, Yusuf?
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~你给我安排了什么健身计划吗，Yusuf？

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Get in position above the tracks, man. I'll see you soon.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~在轨道上面等着跳下去，兄弟。一会儿见。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~What the fuck, man? I got to go in.
~z~Yo, yo, yo. Easy, amigo. I'm just pleased to see you. Come on baby, give me some skin! Come on.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~冷静，好兄弟。我只是见到你很激动。快点宝贝，击个掌！来吧。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~You treat all the commuters like this?
~z~Y'know the sales sheet's going to say,
~z~What you want a subway train for?
~z~We'll have a lounge on the moon by the time we're done. For real.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~我们死之前一定会在月球上开一家酒吧。我说真的。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Things have a tendency to get outta hand man. Maybe you could give me some more exploding shells for peace of mind.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~不怕一万就怕万一。能不能给我点爆炸子弹，我好安心点。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Of course it is. I have this shit calculated to the hundredth decimal fucking point.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~当然简单了。我的方案精准到他妈的百分位。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~All work and no play makes Yusuf a dull boy. Come on, baby, it'll be fun.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~只工作不玩耍，Yusuf也变傻。来吧宝贝，保证有意思。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~I'm talking luxury on a whole new level.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~在奢侈上达到了全新的高度。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Hey, bro. Just in case you mind if I hit you for some of them exploding shells? Thanks, man.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，兄弟。以防万一，你不介意我拿你点爆炸子弹吧？谢了，伙计。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Shit, actually, it's best that we go to the Algonquin Bridge first. The helicopter can wait.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，实际上，我们最好先去Algonquin大桥。直升机放一放。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~If it's our playground, how come I'm the only one getting dirty? Shit.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~如果是「我们」的游乐场，怎么脏活累活都是我的？操。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~We're taking that shit out to the Gulf for a new Liberty City themed development out there.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~把这东西弄到海湾地区，开发一个自由城主题的新项目。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~How you feel about helping this Arabic sonofabitch steal himself an LTA subway car?
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~帮这个阿拉伯人偷一辆LTA列车你觉得怎么样？

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~This place going to be so expensive, people won't even be able to afford it.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~这地方会卖出天价，普通人绝对买不起。
~z~神迹，兄弟。这他妈简直就是神迹。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Slight change of plan, I'll get the chopper later. Head out to the east side of the Algonquin Bridge, homie.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~计划有变，飞机晚点再拿。先去Algonquin大桥的东侧。

E2Y4AUD.original: ~z~Get that shit going through a precious and delicate coral reef! Ah! Perfect.
E2Y4AUD.translated: ~z~让它穿过一片美丽珍贵的珊瑚礁！啊！完美。
